Map Name: scoutknifez_helicopter
Version: 1.0

Description: Got Pro Texturez! Dev FTW!
Quite a Small map. But the fact that its small, makes it fast and rapid! Just how scouts are!
Can you make your way up to the Plane with 2 other members of your team?
- 1 Driver
- 1 M2 Sprayer!

Special Thanks to : Smurfii For making the Plane Prefab!
http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/1716

Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!

www.hellclan.co.uk

Made by : ]HeLL[ Kyanite
